msgid "This document provides instructions on setting up ODK Aggregate using `Apache Tomcat <http://tomcat.apache.org/>`_ and `MySQL <https://www.mysql.com/>`_ on a Linux micro-instance on the `Amazon Web Services <https://aws.amazon.com/>`_  `EC2 infrastructure <https://aws.amazon.com/ec2/>`_."
